des:
Chart Toppers is YOUR Hit Music Station! From Taylor Swift, Ed Sheeran, Bruno Mars, Adele, Pink and Green Day to Michael Jackson, Whitney Houston, Madonna and Prince - if it was a hit song, it plays here.

Whether you grew up dancing to the music of the 80's and 90's or cruised around cranking up the pop music in the 2000's and today - My Hits is the very best of pop, dance, rock, techno, adult contemporary, r&b and urban. The absolute best mix of the biggest songs from the biggest artists.
